.SH NAME
.PP
box - A tool for creating text boxes in the terminal


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBbox [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Box is a CLI tool for creating text boxes in the terminal.
It supports various themes, colors, and nested boxes.


